Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:47.96,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Dauntless courage and a pioneering spirit.}Lòng dũng cảm và tinh thần xông pha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.84,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{It's Adler dorm for you.}Nhà Adler.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:54.26,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Hmm. You have strong magical power,\Nradical ideas, and a challenging nature.}Ma lực mạnh mẽ, ý tưởng thú vị và thách thức mọi thứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:56.22,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{You belong in Lang dorm.}Cậu thuộc nhà Lang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:01.97,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Heh. Centuries have passed\Nsince I was given this role.}{\i0}Nhiều thế kỉ đã qua từ khi ta được giao vai trò này.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:06.77,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Not once have I misjudged,\Nas I can read people's thoughts.}{\i0}Chưa từng một lần sai làm. Ta có thể đọc suy nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.90,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{- Now, keep them coming!\N- Next, Mash Burnedead.}Tiếp, Mash Burnedead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:10.11,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{'Kay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:22.58,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Oh, I need to control my power. Sorry.}Chết, phải kiểm soát sức mạnh. Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:23.91,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Freaky.}{\i0}Đáng sợ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:26.54,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Wait, he's only thinking\Nabout cream puffs.}{\i0}Khoan, nhóc này chỉ toàn nghĩ đến su kem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.58,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What's with this guy?}{\i0}Tên nào thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.00,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Isn't there anything\Nother than cream puffs?}{\i0}Ngoài su kem không còn gì khác à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:34.51,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Seriously, what are you thinking about?\NWhat's with that face?}{\i0}Cậu ta nghĩ gì vậy? Cái mặt đó là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:39.43,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No, this is bad. Several centuries\Ninto dorm selection at our academy,}{\i0}Không ổn... Vài thế kỉ chọn lựa của ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.93,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{not once have I\Nbeen stumped for an answer.}{\i0}chưa lần nào ta không đưa ra câu trả lời...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:45.43,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Okay, let's try this again.}{\i0}Thử lại xem nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:48.35,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Bliss.}{\i0}Hạnh phúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:54.82,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{A cream puff is a confection\Nwhere batter is baked into a hollow shell}Bánh su kem là một loại bánh nướng có nhân là kem tươi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:57.99,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{and custard cream is packed\Ninto the empty space inside.}và hỗn hợp trứng sữa được đưa vào bên trong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:19:01.24,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Especially for Choux Au Craquelin,\Nwhere gooey cream fills a brittle shell.}Đặc biệt đối với Choux Au Craquelin,\Nnơi kem béo ngậy lấp đầy lớp vỏ giòn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.78,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{And if one were to make an analogy\Nwith humans, it's someone}Nếu so sánh với con người thì sẽ là
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:05.16,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{- harboring kindness within strength—\N- It's suddenly gotten eloquent!}một kẻ chứa đựng lòng tốt cùng sức mạnh--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.79,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Cream puff lovers go to Adler!}Người yêu bánh su kem thuộc nhà Adler!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:10.79,Mashle,,0,0,0,,Cái gì hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.42,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{'Kay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:15.38,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah, there was that.}Có nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.38,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So that was...}{\i0}Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.38,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{- Mash.\N- This guy.}{\i0}Thằng này...\N Mash...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.55,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I see.}{\i0}Ra là thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:20.89,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Ahem.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:24.18,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Lang's elite, the Magia Lupus,}Đám cấp cao của Lang, Magia Lupus,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:26.93,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{are a group\Nof seven distinguished students.}là một nhóm 7 tên ưu tú.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:29.94,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{That Pierced Eyebrow\Nmust be one of their lackeys.}Tên xỏ khuyên vừa nãy là cấp dưới của chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.56,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{They've been grabbing up coins\Nto sway who the Divine Visionary will be.}Chúng giành giật những đồng xu của những ai có mang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.94,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Since you have a coin...}Vì ngươi đã có 1 xu vàng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:42.36,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{keep your distance from Lang,\Nand stick with dormmates whenever you can.}Hãy tránh xa nhà Lang bằng mọi giá.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:44.66,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Okay. I will.}Được.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:48.20,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But Lance's warning was in vain...}{\i0}Nhưng lời cảnh báo của Lance là vô ích.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:50.92,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and Mash found himself lost in school.}{\i0}Và Mash đã đi lạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:54.04,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Where's the next class?}Tiết sau ở đâu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:58.42,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Here it is, I think.}Đây rồi. Chắc thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:01.68,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Should I push or pull to open this door?}Mình nên mở hay kéo nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.39,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Hmm.}Xem nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.22,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{I always get it wrong.}Lúc nào mình cũng lộn cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:11.19,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Do I push or pull? Hmm...}Mở hay kéo nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.10,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{I-I'm sorry!}T-Tôi vô cùng xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.69,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{I'm terribly sorry!}Vô cùng xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:18.65,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Look, you said you wanted to join us,}Mày nói muốn tham gia bọn tao,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:21.99,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{and that's why Lord Abel\Ngave you a chance.}và ngài Abel đã cho cơ hội.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:25.16,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Furthermore, you let Adler take a coin.}Và mày để lũ Adler lấy mất xu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:28.20,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{O-Once more! Please give me one more chan—}L-Lần nữa! Xin hãy cho tôi thêm 1 cơ hội.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:29.16,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{You misunderstand.}Mày hiểu lầm gì rồi thì phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:30.50,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.83,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{I gave a chance?}Ta cho cơ hội?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:36.84,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{That makes it sound\Nlike I expected something out of him.}Cứ như ta đang kì vọng gì vào ngươi vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.88,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Oh, man, sorry 'bout that.}Tôi rất xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.88,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Humans worthy\Nof making this world go round...}Những kẻ xứng đáng dẫn dắt thế giới...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:45.59,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{must be chosen individuals.}phải là những kẻ được chọn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:51.60,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Perfect education.\NOverwhelming talent. Noble bloodline.}Nền giáo dục hoàn hảo. Sức mạnh \Náp đảo. Dòng máu thuần chủng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:58.02,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{We're collecting coins\Nto create a world free of impurities.}Chúng ta thu thập xu để thanh lọc thế giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.40,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{But what about you?}Nhưng còn ngươi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:05.24,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{You can't even become\Na sacrificial pawn for our objective.}Thậm chí không đủ khả năng làm con chốt thí.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:08.45,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Pathetic wretch. You have my sympathy.}Tội nghiệp thay. Ta thương cảm với ngươi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:12.91,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{It must be hard to go on living,\Nknowing that you're worthless.}Hẳn là phải khó khăn lắm khi sống tiếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:15.67,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{But rest assured.}Nhưng yên tâm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:21.63,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{You no longer need to think\Nabout such things.}Ngươi không cần phải suy nghĩ gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:35.64,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{The Divine Visionary should be me.}Kẻ được chọn sẽ là ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:38.23,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Not some riffraff from Adler.}Chứ không phải lũ rác rưởi Adler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:41.78,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Right...}Nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:43.07,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Mother?}Mẹ yêu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.74,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{A world free of impurities.}Thế giới thuần chủng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:48.32,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{It will be my—}Con sẽ--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:50.28,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:54.58,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{I couldn't figure out\Nwhether to push or pull this door open.}Tôi thắc mắc không biết nên mở hay kéo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:55.41,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Sorry.}Xin lỗi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:59.67,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Also, you know\Nthat's a doll you're talking to?}Với cả... anh đang nói chuyện với búp bê à?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:03.76,Mashle,,0,0,0,,{Thank you\Nfor bringing that to my attention.}Cảm ơn vì đã chú ý.
